WEBVTT

00:11.312 --> 00:12.411
[man] <i> Brother.</i>

00:14.515 --> 00:15.614
<i>Brother.</i>

00:17.284 --> 00:18.384
<i>Brother.</i>

00:19.787 --> 00:22.321
<i>Maybe the most
beautiful word ever.</i>

00:24.258 --> 00:28.594
<i>Aaron... Aaron,
I never dreamed anyone could care.</i>

00:30.264 --> 00:31.363
<i>This one...</i>

00:32.333 --> 00:35.534
<i>This is the most beautiful.</i>

00:37.038 --> 00:38.504
<i>And I have you to thank.</i>

00:40.000 --> 00:46.074
